          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">The only platform where you can learn directly from three world champions—each revealing their signature, championship-winning systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-bg border-4 border-primary/20">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" /></svg>
