          <h3 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text-primary">Lifetime Access, No Subscriptions</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">Enjoy lifetime access to a premium, structured curriculum. Your courses are yours forever, with no recurring fees, so you can learn at your own pace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-text-primary">Crystal Clear Instruction</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">Understand complex shots instantly with multi-angle 4K streaming and laser-guided graphics that illustrate the perfect line, lead, and break point for every target.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-bg border-4 border-primary/20">
            <!--<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-24 w-24 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.042 21.672L13.684 16.6m0 0l-2.51 2.225.569-9.47 5.227 7.917-3.286-.672zM12 2.25a.75.75 0 01.75.75v.008l.008.008.008.008.008.008.008.008.008.008h.008a.75.75 0 010 1.5h-.008l-.008-.008L12 4.5l-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008-.008v-.008A.75.75 0 0112 2.25z" /></svg>-->
            <img src="public/assets/images/cti_instruct_icon.jpeg">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

